      "@id": "pfl:ThreeHorizonsModel",
      "@type": "rdfs:Class",
      "name": "ThreeHorizonsModel",
      "rdfs:subClassOf": "schema:Intangible",
      "description": "McKinsey Three Horizons — structures innovation investment across H1 (core optimization, 0-12mo), H2 (emerging opportunities, 12-36mo), H3 (transformational bets, 36mo+). Maps to VSOM time horizons: H1=Objectives, H2=Strategy, H3=Vision. Investment split (typically 70/20/10) drives PPM portfolio allocation.",
